#

Autumn Spice Pumpkin Buns

$12.5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 60%
Servings: 12

Allergens:

glutendairyeggs

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Tags:

bakedsweetfall

Description

Indulge in these soft, spiced pumpkin buns drizzled with a rich cream cheese glaze, perfect for a cozy fall treat.

Ingredients

  • All-purpose flour: 4 cups
  • Pumpkin puree: 1 cup
  • Granulated sugar: 1/3 cup
  • Brown sugar: 1/3 cup
  • Unsalted butter: 1/4 cup
  • Milk: 1/4 cup
  • Eggs: 2 large
  • Yeast: 2 1/4 tsp
  • Salt: 1 tsp
  • Pumpkin pie spice: 2 tsp
  • Cinnamon: 1 tsp
  • Cream cheese: 4 oz
  • Powdered sugar: 1 cup
  • Vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • Heavy cream: 2 tbsp
